textRun.content: Every year since I met your Oma Dianne I have been obsessed with her cheesecake cookies. They are my favorite thing on Christmas morning. Oma Dianne started making for any important gathering because she knew I would be so happy to have them. I hope that they bring you joy and if they don’t then please make them with love for others.I love you dearly.
⅓ cup firmly packed brown sugar
Cream butter, brown sugar and flour in blender
Stir in pecans (reserve ½ c of this mixture for the topping)
Press remainder into bottom of and 8 in square baking pan
Cool, and when cooled spread with jelly
Cream the cream cheese and sugar
Slowly add in lemon juice and vanilla extract
Pour over bott and sprinkle with the reserved topping mixture
